8. sakta (an adverb modifying "ruttnar")
9. men (a conjunction)
10. säkert (an adverb modifying "ruttnar")
11. sönder (an adverb modifying "ruttnar")
12. av (a preposition introducing a complement)
13. det (a pronoun as subject of "förändrade")
14. förändrade (a past participle modifying "klimatet")
